    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a pot with 15g <span class=\"text-purple\">[25g]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[30g]</span> <strong>butter </strong>over a medium heat and cook for 1 min or until melted</p><p>Once melted, add 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [1 1/2 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong> and cook for 1 min or until a sandy paste remains</p><p>Gradually whisk in the<strong> stock </strong>and cook for 5-6 min or until thickened – this is your<strong> gravy</strong></p>",
